data.description: MLS# 270806 NOW FINISHED! This beautiful luxury townhome built by Brett Lott Homes could be yours! Shy of 1700 Sq Ft, 3 bed, 1.75 bath, 2 car garage. This beauty includes laminate flooring, quartz counters, steel gas appliances, front & back yard landscaping and block wall fencing. Luxury details such as lighting, cabinets, tile backsplash, hardware & much more. Located in the rapidly growing "West Village" right by the Country Mercantile off of Dallas Rd. Call your favorite realtor & inquire about the builder incentive offered on this home!
